Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,千代有收過什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.50,0:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.74,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我是...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.44,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,簽名...吧
